Jan 29 (Reuters) - Starhill Global Real Estate Investment Trust:
* ‍DPU FOR 2Q FY17/18 WAS 1.17 CENTS​ * ‍QTRLY GROSS REVENUE S$52.5 MILLION VERSUS S$54.1​ MILLION
* ‍QTRLY NET PROPERTY INCOME S$40.5 MILLION VERSUS S$41.4​ MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
